_sText:
I decided to make a fight yard map, and so here it is! 
This is a simple and small FY-indoor map, the players will fight in corridors. 
I hope you will enjoy playing this map. 

Map contains 24 players and 12 weapons on the ground at each spawn zone (CT and T).

Don't edit this map without my permission! 

Thx to Chrazini for his prefab "Beautiful Letters"!
